    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[sqlite 插入性能优化]]></title>
      <url>http://yoursite.com/2016/05/20/sqlite-%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- MarkdownTOC -->
<ul>
<li>sqlite配置调整</li>
<li>手动提交事务</li>
<li>Prepared Statements</li>
<li>批量插入</li>
<li>多线程</li>
</ul>
<!-- /MarkdownTOC -->
<p>本文源于工作中的测试，并参考<a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/1711631/improve-insert-per-second-performance-of-sqlite" title="impove performace of sqlite" target="_blank" rel="external">improve insert-per-second performace of SQLite</a></p>
<h2 id="sqlite配置调整"><a href="#sqlite配置调整" class="headerlink" title="sqlite配置调整"></a>sqlite配置调整</h2><p>使用journal_mode=memory或off，存在一定风险<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pragma synchronous=OFF</span><br><span class="line">pragma journal_mode=memory</span><br><span class="line">pragma page_size=16000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="手动提交事务"><a href="#手动提交事务" class="headerlink" title="手动提交事务"></a>手动提交事务</h2><p>sqlite自动提交事务<br><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sqlite3_exec(dbInst, <span class="string">"begin transaction"</span>, <span class="literal">NULL</span>, <span class="literal">NULL</span>, <span class="literal">NULL</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//insert/update/replace 语句</span></span><br><span class="line">sqlite3_exec(dbInst, <span class="string">"commit transaction"</span>, <span class="literal">NULL</span>, <span class="literal">NULL</span>, <span class="literal">NULL</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="Prepared-Statements"><a href="#Prepared-Statements" class="headerlink" title="Prepared Statements"></a>Prepared Statements</h2><p><code>sqlite3_exec</code>内部调用的<code>prepared statement</code>，直接使用<code>prepared statement</code>效率高。<br><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sqlite3_stmt* stmt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">char</span> sqlFormat[] = <span class="string">"replace into tabName values(?, ?, ?)"</span></span><br><span class="line">sqlite3_prepare_v2(dbInst, sqlFormat, <span class="number">-1</span>, &amp;stmt, <span class="literal">NULL</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    sqlite3_bind_int(stmt, <span class="number">1</span>, intVal);</span><br><span class="line">    sqlite3_bind_text(stmt, <span class="number">2</span>, strBuffer, bufferLen, <span class="literal">NULL</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//sqlite3_bind_text(stmt, 2, strBuffer, bufferLen, SQLITE_STATIC)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//sqlite_static表明你bind的内存地址到sql执行一直有效</span></span><br><span class="line">    sqlite3_bind_blob(stmt, <span class="number">3</span>, binaryValue, valueLen, SQLITE_STAITC);</span><br><span class="line">    sqlite3_step(stmt);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//如果不包含blob可以直接使用sqlite3_reset</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//sqlite3_reset(stmt);</span></span><br><span class="line">    sqlite3_clear_bindings(stmt);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">sqlite3_finalize(stmt);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="批量插入"><a href="#批量插入" class="headerlink" title="批量插入"></a>批量插入</h2><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">insert</span> <span class="keyword">into</span> tabName (column1, column2, column3) <span class="keyword">values</span> (<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">3</span>), (<span class="number">4</span>,<span class="number">5</span>,<span class="number">6</span>),(<span class="number">7</span>,<span class="number">8</span>,<span class="number">9</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>sqlite 3.7.11以下版本<br><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">insert</span> <span class="keyword">into</span> tabName </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="string">'value1'</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> column1, <span class="string">'value2'</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> column2, <span class="string">'value3'</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> column3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">union</span> all <span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="string">'value1'</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> column1, <span class="string">'value2'</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> column2, <span class="string">'value3'</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> column3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">union</span> all <span class="keyword">select</span> <span class="string">'value1'</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> column1, <span class="string">'value2'</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> column2, <span class="string">'value3'</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> column3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="多线程"><a href="#多线程" class="headerlink" title="多线程"></a>多线程</h2><p>如果使用多线程，可以考虑<code>shared pager cache</code>节省磁盘IO<br><a href="http://sqlite.org/sharedcache.html" title="shared-cahe mode" target="_blank" rel="external">sqlite shared-cache mode</a><br><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sqlite3* dbPtr=<span class="literal">NULL</span>;</span><br><span class="line">sqlite3_open_v2(dbname, &amp;dbPtr, SQLITE_OPEN_READWRITE | SQLITE_OPEN_CREATE|SQLITE_OPEN_SHAREDCACHE)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    
