      <title><![CDATA[git filename too long]]></title>
      <url>http://yoursite.com/2016/05/20/git-filename-too-long/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>由于windows操作系统限制，git bash for windows 有时会出现filename too long的问题<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global core.longpaths true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>完美解决</p>
]]></content>
